Effective Date: 11 June 2023

Our Mausam - Nepal Weather App ("App") is designed to provide users with up-to-date weather information and forecasts. This Privacy Policy outlines how we handle user data and ensures your privacy is protected when using our App.

Information Collection and Usage:
1.1 No Personally Identifiable Information (PII) or Personal Data Collection: Our App does not require any sign-in, login, or registration, and we do not collect any personally identifiable information such as your name, email address, phone number, or location data.

1.2 Non-Personal Data Collection: While using the App, we may collect non-personal information such as your device's unique identifier (e.g., Android Advertising ID), device model, operating system version, language preferences, and other technical information. This data is used solely to improve the functionality and performance of the App and to provide you with a better user experience.

Location Information:
2.1 No Location Data Collection: Our App does not collect or access your precise location information. We do not require access to your device's GPS, Wi-Fi, or network-based location services. Therefore, we do not track or store your location data.

Data Sharing:
3.1 Third-Party Services: Our App does not share any data with third-party services, including advertisers, analytics providers, or other external entities. We are committed to protecting your privacy, and we do not engage in any data monetization practices.

Security:
4.1 Data Security Measures: We take reasonable measures to protect the data collected through the App from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction. We use industry-standard security practices to safeguard the data.

Children's Privacy:
5.1 Our App is not intended for use by individuals under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect any personal information from children. If we discover that we have inadvertently collected personal information from a child under 13, we will promptly delete such data from our systems.

Changes to Privacy Policy:
6.1 We reserve the right to modify or update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be effective immediately upon posting the revised Privacy Policy in the App. We encourage you to review this Privacy Policy periodically to stay informed about our data practices.

Contact Us:
7.1 If you have any questions or concerns regarding this Privacy Policy or our data practices, please contact us at [contact email address].

By using our Mausam - Nepal Weather App, you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agreed to the terms of this Privacy Policy.

Note: This privacy policy is a general template and should be customized to accurately reflect the practices and policies of your specific app.
